By NakkiMaisteri


MAP BRIEFING

After a horrible murder at women locker room a taliban ghost started to haunt the place. The whole building had to be shutten down. The local terrorist "gang" heard about this incident they decided to blow up the whole building. While they were making their assault a counter terrorist force just happened to be inspecting the area. Are you alone?

OBJECTIVE
Terrorists: Plant the bomb in one out of three "sauna", area on the map and destroy the building along with the ghost.
Counter terrorists: Protect the sauna from demolition by all cost!

MAP INFORMATION

Map contains: "Ability to run outside / Scary place / secret areas / ETC"
Recommented players/Max players: 20/40
Map contains three bomb site.
Spawnpoints: Terrorists spawn from trucks at both exits of the building. Counter terrorists spawn from locker room close to the bomb zones.
All of the map, isn't in the screenshots, EXPLORE!

Download --> Test --> Comment --> Rate.

Kittehs will thank you!

This is my first released map and my seconds zombie escape map ever! It took me about 2 months to make with the help of the StoneCold clan. You start of at a yard kinda place and you can choose 3 roads; 1: To the right up a staircase. 2: Trough a door in the house and up through the house. 3: To the left and through a wall. The 3 roads will lead you to an abandon warehouse. The 1st road will lead you to the top of the warehouse where you will then have to go to the right on a wall and down a ladder, down there will be waiting a van that will take you to the end bridge. Road 2 and 3 will lead you to the 1st floor of the warehouse and the bottom. You will then go on a train and ride to safety, but unluckily the train get's stuck and you will have to jump on a truck to go to the end bridge. At the end bridge 2 things can happend (chosen randomly every round) : Either the bridge will break and you will go to a dark harbor where you will defend 60 seconds until the boat sails you to safety, or the bridge will not break and you will go into the skyscraper and defend for 100 seconds until the window breaks, you jump out and a nuke goes of and kills all the zombies. There are 3 secrets in the map that you will have to find without help.

The map, like the name says, is not completely finish. I am currently unaware of the Zombie vs Human balance during the complete run, and it may require tweeking as there may well be some few bugs and glitch in the level.

This is the first map I've ever created in Counter Strike: Source. This is my first try as you can see, it's a small zombie map made for small servers such as fe-gaming.net's zombie server. 

I'm going to train and improve allot in the future, it's hard to map (If you ask me) but it's funny. The map might be alittle light but I hope it works out. You don't need to use it if you don't want to but please help me out and tell me what I can fix in it and so on. I've tried fixing the light but it doesn't work even if I delete tons of lights.

You can go ahead and edit this and make something out of it if you want to, I'd be glad if you did it but it's all up to you. Good luck and thanks for checking the map out! Remember to visit my website.

Inspired by Lila's addictive map, zm_lila_panic, I have come across of the thought of remaking it.

And yes, I know there are many remakes out there, but I wanted to test out my skills on remaking it. New textures and bug fixes will be added on the next version!

CREDITS ARE AT THE BOTTOM!

Even though its textures were not changed, (yet) I have added many things:
-Lighting 
-More props
-Decals (graffiti, blood)
-Secret room
-More realistic
-More fun!
I have blocked some parts of the map to prevent "vent camping", such as the cement cylinders. 

Even though the textures aren't that great, upon request, I will make a new version with good textures!
